value.string: Very surprising ocean views from this classic home in Happy Valley! Great lot with home perched against the side of the valley. Needs to be gutted or torn down.

This beautiful spacious two story home has the location and privacy your buyers will love. As you come into the Fairway Estates it is the first left situated at the end of the road abuts large gulch and sits next to the 8th green. Upper level deck has been extended with lovely ocean and mountain views. Hardwood flooring in kitchen and dining room, quick step uniclic floor tiles in living room and bedrooms. Fenced back yard .for privacy and what a peacful feeling to walk out of your master bedroom into your own private gardens.
